etive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΜΙΑΣ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>]Δ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>]ΡΟΝ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΜΙΑΣ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>]Δ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>]ΡΟΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003132_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo from De Miro and Fiorentini 1976-77: tav. 48 fig.3\" src=\"ISic003132_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003132.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo from De Miro and Fiorentini 1976-77: tav. 48 fig.3\" src=\"ISic003132-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text checked against (poor) photograph\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"1\">1: \u003Cspan>DeMiro Fiorentini: ΜΙΑΣ.Δ.[O]ΡΟΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>δῶρον appears the most likely reading of the latter part of the text, but it is very difficult to judge whether one or more letters is missing between Δ and Ρ, and even if a letter is missing at all between Σ and Δ. From the photograph, it seems possible that the letter between Μ and Α could also be a Φ.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 28.0768 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> De Miro and Fiorentini 1976-1977 453 tav.48 fig.3 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002049\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002049\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Small neat letters of square form. From the photograph, it appears the sigma may be fairly open, the alpha with straight bar, and the rho possibly with a tail.\u003C/p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[178,181,184,187,190,193,196,199],{"id":179,"html":180},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΜΙΑΣ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>]Δ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>]ΡΟΝ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"editi